  {day:30,title:"Project & Revision",definition:"Mini project ‡§¨‡§®‡§æ‡§ì ‡§î‡§∞ ‡§™‡•Ç‡§∞‡•á concept ‡§¶‡•ã‡§π‡§∞‡§æ‡§ì‡•§",uses:"Practice",example:`print("Course Completed üéâ")`}
